# NetTester

Open Source Network Test Automation Platform

## Vision

NetTester helps engineers build, execute and diagnose
network device test scenarios without writing code.

## Features

- GUI Scenario Builder
- Action Library
- Network Topology
- Multi-node Execution
- OpenWrt Support
- Linux Support
- AI Test Review

## Roadmap

- [ ] MVP
- [ ] GUI
- [ ] Action Registry
- [ ] Scenario Builder
- [ ] AI Assistant
